{"tid":955584,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"廣西發展商賣樓出奇招　女模裸背畫樓盤平面圖","createTime":"2018-12-25T13:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T02:19:52.000Z","uid":66271,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3096f708042a0b213c8499954fbe9e3a0a523dce","tid":955584,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T13:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://wongyau.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/2312123.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwongyau.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F2312123.jpg&h=42a49b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2158763/org/6aeeb256458e45558feee3464309d521.JPG/Olod8ja1X9r1KQ188sSXmKploWN8q6KDKbKsPSmyrD0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2158763%2Forg%2F6aeeb256458e45558feee3464309d521.JPG%2FOlod8ja1X9r1KQ188sSXmKploWN8q6KDKbKsPSmyrD0&h=c03927f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣西南寧市近日一個樓盤展銷會為求吸引買家，可算無所不用其極。發展商竟在展銷會上聘用數名幾乎赤裸上身的女模，並在她們的後背上畫上單位的平面圖，而女模的胸前則被寫上樓盤的名稱。<br />\n<br />\n涉事樓盤項目名稱為「南站新城」，發展商為南寧偉潤投資有限責任公司。從網傳片段可見，數名身材高挑、上身幾乎赤裸的女模排成一排，展示着胸前彩繪上方「南站新城」4個字和背上標號、形狀各不相同的樓盤平面圖，但被網民炮轟低俗。<br />\n<br />\n據發展商多名銷售職員指，活動屬公司策劃部安排作為樓盤的暖場活動，目前活動已經結束，是否繼續進行尚不得而知。對於這場具爭議性的樓盤宣傳活動，江南區工商局商標廣告股負責人回應指，已注意到有關情況，但認為該宣傳活動並沒有涉及虛假宣傳、誇大其詞，故不屬於虛假廣告，至於是否低俗涉黃，應由警方查處界定。江南區住建局和工業園區管委會則表示，此事不歸其管理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LEZdT6jbXiQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLEZdT6jbXiQ&d=EAYqXrIIJPGx4S0IDbeNMghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=d923a945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LEZdT6jbXiQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300227171a41f3387d42c3e680794a3fee44f04d","tid":955584,"uid":17429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:00:07.000Z","msg":"又黎"},{"pid":"24bbe6252c783b6b3946e7f93bd2efd1abe88398","tid":955584,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:01:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"028ff2b4650f459260019b0b75b476decc05486e","tid":955584,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24bbe6252c783b6b3946e7f93bd2efd1abe88398","tid":955584,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:01:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:01:51.000Z","msg":"香港幾時跟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0042d3bbebeac87fd19d028911b55548ad1f57ae","tid":955584,"uid":38651,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"028ff2b4650f459260019b0b75b476decc05486e","tid":955584,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24bbe6252c783b6b3946e7f93bd2efd1abe88398","tid":955584,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:01:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:01:51.000Z","msg":"香港幾時跟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:02:35.000Z","msg":"正面畫平面圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8049bf3a2b248dfcf489241f121492cf26c8d15","tid":955584,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:02:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fef195235ea3d2a96eceefbe367a9cee866f9515","tid":955584,"uid":66271,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0042d3bbebeac87fd19d028911b55548ad1f57ae","tid":955584,"uid":38651,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"028ff2b4650f459260019b0b75b476decc05486e","tid":955584,"uid":66271,"like":0,"disl